umber or othermethod of unique identification.\",\"description\":\"9.9.1.a Examine the list of devices to verify it includes:\\u2022 Make model of device\\u2022 Location of device (for example the address of the site orfacility where the device is located)\\u2022 Device serial number or other method of uniqueidentification.9.9.1.b Select a sample of devices from the list and observedevices and device locations to verify that the list is accurateand up to date. 9.9.1.c Interview personnel to verify the list of devices isupdated when devices are added relocated decommissionedetc.\",\"audit_questionaire\":\"Keeping an up-to-date list of devices helps anorganization keep track of where devices aresupposed to be and quickly identify if a device ismissing or lost.The method for maintaining a list of devices maybe automated (for example a device-managementsystem) or manual (for example documented inelectronic or paper records). For on-the-roaddevices the location may include the name of thepersonnel to whom the device is assigned.\",\"compliance_package_id\":6,\"workflow_owner_id\":null,\"workflow_status\":0,\"created\":\"2023-01-18T13:19:22+00:00\",\"modified\":\"2023-01-18T13:19:22+00:00\",\"deleted\":0,\"deleted_date\":null}',0,0,NULL,'Admin Admin','1',NULL,6,'192.168.23.1','/compliance-package-items/add?modalId=1&_=1674047869066&ImportTool=1','2023-01-18 13:19:22'),('75a84726-4600-473c-9241-d26b11c73713',1,'CREATE',NULL,'CompliancePackageItems','62','a0751f76-f22a-4748-b58d-9cb1f260ecba','{\"id\":62,\"item_id\":\"9.1.0\",\"name\":\"Use appropriate facility entry controls to limit and monitor physical access to systems in the cardholder data environment.\",\"description\":\"NA\",\"audit_questionaire\":\"NA\",\"compliance_package_id\":18,\"workflow_owner_id\":null,\"workflow_status\":0,\"created\":\"2023-01-18T13:19:43+00:00\",\"modified\":\"2023-01-18T13:19:43+00:00\",\"deleted\":0,\"deleted_date\":null}',0,0,NULL,'Admin Admin','1',NULL,6,'192.168.23.1','/compliance-pac